profile:
Save thousands by dealing directly with a manufacturer! Canadian Choice Windows and Doors Inc. is a leading manufacturer of windows in Canada, serving Ontario. Canadian Choice Windows and Doors offers a huge selection of replacement windows including energy efficient windows, vinyl windows, casement windows, awning windows and bow and bay windows.

Canadian Choice Windows and Doors has been serving Toronto, Richmond Hill, North York, Markham, Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Kitchener, Cambridge, Niagra Falls and the surrounding areas as well as in Calgary, Edmonton, Winnipeg and Northern Ontario. 

Why is Canadian Choice Windows and Doors your best solution for window replacement?

1. No Pressure Estimate: take your time & make informed decision

2. Save Money: Energy Star windows will reduce your energy bill by 30 %

3. Professional Installation: flawless installation and thorough clean up by courteous installers

4. High Quality: The highest quality windows in the industry, featuring foam injected honey comb structure.
 
5. Easy Financing: Financing solutions to fit anyone’s lifestyle

6. Maximum Comfort: low-E coating to reflect summer sun and retain winter heat with our Cardinal Smart Glass system.

7. Zero Maintenance: our windows are easy to clean from within the home and will never fade or discolor

Canadian Choice Windows and Doors is your smartest solution for window and door replacement.

profile:
Our History
 
Verdun Windows and Doors has been proudly serving the Ottawa-Carleton region since 1982. Before the doors opened, we laid out 4 key core principles to our business that we constantly recommit ourselves to:
- Integrity our reputation is based on it. We have a genuine appreciation for your business and patronage. 
- Honesty in everything we do. This is the only way to build trust with our customers. 
- Efficiency in every aspect of our business. From manufacturing, to sales, to installation, to the follow up post sale. 
- Accuracy whether we’re pricing a job out for you, or measuring on an installation, accuracy ensures that no surprises come up inconveniently. 
 
Where We Are Today and Our Future - 38 years later and growing…
200 employees 
42,000 square foot one-of-a-kind manufacturing facility in Ottawa 
The largest installation team in the Ottawa-Carleton region for residential window replacements and new installations 
National industry leading organization 
Our future doesn’t include just being content with our industry-leading reputation. Part of our success has been a constant re-commitment to the principles which have brought us to where we are today. When you give us the opportunity to earn your business, we take that trust very seriously and appreciate it — the same way we did over 38 years ago.

profile:
Landmark Home Solutions have been supplying comfort and peace of mind to homeowners across Ontario since 1987. We’re proud to offer one of the most energy efficient windows available on the market today that offers homeowners a significant return on investment all while being backed with the strongest warranty in the business today!
 
We’re part of the Canadian Standards Association (CSA) and the Better Business Bureau, and in all the years we’ve been in business, we’ve never had an unresolved complaint. We’re members of SAWDAC (Siding and Window Dealers Association of Canada) and make sure that we meet their membership criteria, code of ethics and sign an ironclad five-year workmanship guarantee statement.
 
We’re also proud to say that our windows are Energy Star certified.  As you probably know, the international Energy Star symbol is a simple way for consumers to identify products that are among the most energy-efficient on the market. We also offer financing through TD Canada Trust, ensuring that our customers have a trustworthy partner too.
Based in St. Catharines, Ontario, 

Landmark Home Solutions is proud to represent our Canadian heritage in all that we do.  Our windows are made right here, so you know you’re getting the best quality windows in the world.

profile:
DALMEN PRO IS YOUR OTTAWA WINDOWS & DOORS EXPERTS "BUILT FOR COMFORT, INSTALLED WITH CARE"

You can count on Dalmen Pro experts to securely install and seal your new windows. Not only are all our window products high-quality, but they are Energy Star rated.

With such a diverse variety of Door options for you to choose from, you’ll be sure to find one that suits your wants and needs. All our door products are energy efficient and are custom-built to fit your exact specifications.

Because our installation experts are SAWDAC certified, you can be sure that every installation and service we provide adheres to SAWDAC’s strict guidelines and code of ethics.

Doors and Windows aren’t products that you buy on a consistent basis. They are often a once-in-a-lifetime investment. Our windows and doors are backed by our comprehensive 20/20 warranty (20 years on Product and 20 years on Labour).


We service all of the Greater Ottawa-Gatineau region, including, but not limited to: Aylmer, Brockville, Calabogie, Carleton Place, Cornwall, Hull, Kanata, Orleans, Ottawa, Perth, Renfrew, Smiths Falls and Stittsville.

profile:
Glass Expression is an Ottawa based company who has been Operating since 1995 with humble beginnings. Over time, we have expanded and became a must in our field for any home owner who wishes to increase the level of privacy and/or enhance the look of their existing door system and windows.

What we do
We install standard and custom size decorative seal units of wrought iron or stained glass for exterior doors, sidelites, transoms or any other windows of all size and shapes. We also replace thermo pane and install integrated blinds. Click here to view our whole range of services.

Our mobile show room will allow you to appreciate our wide variety of glass design. Our shop at home innovative approach makes us unique in our field.

Whether your home is old or new, big or small, contemporary or Colonial, finding a glass style for your front door and/or windows, which compliments your home, is important. We have designs that are simple to intricate, clear to obscure. This is where solid metals, textured and beveled glass come together to create true works of art.

Everyone is different and so are our decorative door and window glass designs. Let us help you create a front entrance door that will be the focal point of your home and a true reflection of your taste and style.

Our low cost operating structure and our exclusive partnering with leading manufacturers, allows us to offer a great and unique product at a very competitive price. Shop and compare! Glass Expression is the number one choice to make a statement at a price you can afford!

Along with our estimates and professional advice; we also install our products with a ten year warranty.
services:
Thermal Pane Replacement
Door Cutting
Decorative glass windows and transom windows
Integrated blinds for doors

profile:
“Engineering excellence, built in Canada and Germany”
 
We are proud to serve you in four languages: English, French, German & Russian
 
Our specialty is, to supply home owners and contractors with precise solutions that are beautifully crafted, energy efficient and fit their budgets. Having been in the windows and doors industry since 1986, we appreciate the hard work that goes into every little detail of manufacturing windows, patio doors and entry door systems.
 
From German windows to your north American windows, we carry the complete line of products for your convenience.
 
All our products are manufactured with "German" precision that ensure proper operating for many years to come!
 
We start by evaluating your needs, product selection for your home, while keeping your budget in mind.
 
Our job does not end just because you purchased products from us. 
 
We guide you through the product selection process, re-measure steps, installation procedures to completion of your project and take very good care of you if you need after sale service.
 
We are also "Wheel Chair" accessible for easy access by all our customers!

profile:
We are an Ottawa-based exterior renovation company with over 15 years of extensive construction experience.
We thrive on traditions passed down from a generation of reliable builders. Our approach is quite simple: Do the job right, the first time. We value the long-term personal relationships we built with our clients through mutual respect and high quality work.
Unlike the big-box companies that keep you on hold for hours and rush the job, our family-owned and operated business makes service our number one priority.
From building custom homes to renovating high-rise buildings, our expertise is extensive. We’ve completed thousands of window and door residential installations and are currently overseeing over 100 ongoing commercial projects with the Ottawa condos, co-ops, multi-family units, City and Government buildings, commercial offices, as well as rentals and new construction, hotels, churches, apartment buildings and custom built homes...
Format Exteriors is the only company in Ottawa area that’s approved by engineers for private, commercial and government projects with our “Premium Installation”.
At Format Exteriors, we service the all of Ottawa and the surrounding area. This includes Kanata, Orleans, Nepean, Gloucester, Carleton Place, Embrun, Limoges and anywhere in between.

profile:
Bonnechere Valley Windows for Professional, Guaranteed Products and Service

Custom manufacture to accommodate any size opening and any type of construction.
Professional installation backed by many years of experience.  We have been successfully satisfying customers since 1987.
Our factory and showroom is located in Eganville nestled in the heart of the Ottawa Valley.
Profiles from the leading Canadian vinyl extruder P.H. Tech.
A variety of window and door styles, including the European Tilt & Turn type.
No-fine-print warranty – your guarantee of our commitment to excellence.
We provide free estimates and will meet with you in your home or our Eganville showroom, weekdays, evenings or weekends.

Serving Ottawa and the Valley
Wherever you are in Ottawa – Centretown, Kanata, Nepean, Barrhaven, Orleans . . .
Or in the Ottawa Valley – Deep River, Petawawa, Pembroke, Barry’s Bay, Eganville, Renfrew, Arnprior . . .
Our professional, friendly staff will meet with you to discuss your requirements.
We are licensed to install in the province of Quebec.

Or visit our Eganville showroom so we can show you the remarkable features of our custom windows and doors.

We're social here:
https://www.facebook.com/bvwindow/?ref=page_internal
products:
As manufacturers and installers, Bonnechere Valley Windows has total control over the quality of your new windows and doors.  We are proud to offer our “No Fine Print” Warranty.

We have been blending Art, Science & Craftsmanship since 1987 to create beautiful windows and doors.  Every member of our team is committed to providing high-quality trouble-free windows and doors for your home or business.

We can combine window and door designs to create one-of-a-kind products that will be beautiful and highly functional.
specialities:
Strong
Miter cut and fusion-welded corners form a single, solid unit that won’t loosen and leak at the corners.

Beautiful
The strength of our system allows for bigger unobstructed openings than any other window system.

Reliable
Strong vinyl profiles will not warp or swell and offer consistent operation and weather-tight seals for many years.

Energy Saving
Sashes are designed for superior thermal insulation. Welded construction and stable seals guard against air leakage.

Easy to Operate
Controls and handles are engineered for effortless operation. Windows and doors are designed for ease of cleaning.

Easy Care
Literally “care free”, our products resist corrosion, never need painting and can be easily cleaned from the inside.
name: Bonnechere Valley Windows & Doors Ltd.

profile:
We have been satisfying customers in eastern Ontario for over 19 years. Prior to that we specialized in multi unit low rise commercial applications only. We love what we do and strive to outperform expectations. At Capital Comfort Windows & Doors we carefully assessed the market to deliver you high quality products for a competitive price, based on the region.
 
Both quality of  the product,  quality of  installation  and quality of service are equally important in a window and door replacement process. We do no cut corners on either of these.
 
Our products are all Energy Star Rated.

Our Installers are experienced in residential and commercial applications. Therefore, we install       everything in accordance with today's building code.

We maintain very low service volume; thus we are very quick to respond to service calls when they do happen.

We approach every job, big or small with the same care and quality service. Enjoy the true Capitals Comfort with our energy efficient, maintenance free products.

profile:
Protex window treatments do so much for you! 

Improve your home and office comfort with our solar films. Privacy is achieved with class and style, using various frosting and decorative solutions. Security films add peace of mind knowing your business and family are safe, and so much more.

Let us improve the places you love the most. When your choose from Protex’s range of architectural films, you are taking care of  your home or office. Our films can ensure the safety and comfort of both your work family and your home family. Whether it is UV protection to stop fading, or a ultra strong layer of security film to keep bad elements out, contact us today and find out more about our incredible flat glass upgrades.

The benefits are endless: Building and home energy management with our solar upgrades that save you money from the first day they are applied through there 20 plus year lifespan. We can eliminate headache-inducing glare from computer screens and TVs. Having a little, or a lot of privacy stops you from looking over your shoulder in your office or house. Anti-Graffiti and security films protect your secure spaces so you can focus on the things that are important to you.

Residential, Commercial and Institutional Service

profile:
PREMIUM EUROPEAN ✔️️ WINDOWS & DOORS company offers a unique opportunity to order and install premium European aluminum, uPVC, wood, and frameless glass constructions made of the world's best European profiles: REYNAERS, SCHUCO, ALUPROF, VEKA, GEALAN & other EU profiles for remarkably low wholesale prices. Our HIGH-TECH manufacturing powers in Germany and Poland produce the highest quality windows, front turn and PIVOT doors, and sliding glass walls with double/triple glazing. 
Despite the premium quality, they are 30% cheaper than the average Canadian costs for the same construction configurations, including delivery. 
We are open for one-time orders and long-term cooperation with private clients, corporate clients, construction companies, dealers, architects, interior/ exterior designers, and local distributors in Canada.
